Rowena

Overview

Full Name: Rowena Faulinbroc

Gender: Female

Race: Half-elf

Class: Sorcerer

Age: Youth

Identifying Marks: Fox Ears. These were gained from a Fox Spirit which taught her magic. Other features can show during wild surges.

Character Sheet: PC Rowena Faulinbroc (Erin).pdf

Motivation and Philosophy

Long Term Aspirations: Grandparents never came home from their last planar trip. Want to find out what happened to them.

Short Term Aspirations: Figure out if she is staying with this new party and why.

Personal Life

Friends: Eckobarch Drall - College friend.

Family: Grandmother Arlen

Grandfather Kelsith

Mother Lawicr

Father Gerriclc

Brother Enna

Possessions

Glass Chess piece - Queen. It is red glass which her grandmother brought back from a trip. She said it has something to do with a girl named Alice.

Identity

Internal: Rowena has a twin brother.

External: Quirky

Kind of Thick

Obsessed with other planes and stories her grandma told.

Background

Backstory: Rowena Backstory
